flowchart TD
    subgraph Data Ingestion
        A[Start: Read Source] --> B{Source Type?}
        B -->|Checkpoint| C[Load Mutation .pkl]
        B -->|PDF/Docs| D[PDFPlumber / Text Loader]
        C --> E[Extract Code & Metrics]
        D --> E
        E --> F[Chunk Text (400 words)]
        F --> G[Generate Embeddings (Code/Text Models)]
        G --> H[Vector Store (ChromaDB)]
    end

    subgraph Runtime Retrieval
        I[LLM Request] --> J{RAG Enabled?}
        J -->|Yes| K[Query Vector Store]
        K --> L[Retrieve Top-K Semantic Matches]
        L --> M[Filter by Accuracy/Params]
        M --> N[Format Context Prompt]
        N --> O[Append to Original Prompt]
        J -->|No| O
        O --> P[Send to LLM]
    end

    subgraph Storage
        H
    end

    style H fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style O fill:#ff9,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
